author: ivaynberg
msg: making this non-final so that other behaviors can override and select their default versioned/unversioned requirement. for example for timer behaviors it is important to be unversioned, while for all others it is important to be versioned. this way the timer behaviors can override this method and return an unversioned url

author: ivaynberg
msg: unversioned ajax urls are causing problems if the backbutton is used, so i am changing the default behavior to use versioned urls for now. i think in the end it will end up being a safer default. will be investigating this further today.
